    <item>
      <title>永续债券不太可能成为 YPF 案中负债累累的阿根廷的答案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/perpetual-bonds-unlikely-to-be-the-answer-for-indebted-argentina</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 建议阿根廷可以发行债务，以遵守与石油公司 YPF 国有化相关的 160 亿美元诉讼裁决，但这一建议遭到了多次被连续违约者伤害的投资者的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/perpetual-bonds-unlikely-to-be-the-answer-for-indebted-argentina</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 19:41:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国传奇就三文鱼交易起诉在美国的智利投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/china-s-legend-sues-chilean-investor-in-us-over-salmon-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利鲑鱼养殖商 Australis Seafoods 的中国母公司在美国提起的诉讼中表示，前所有者伊西多罗·基罗加 (Isidoro Quiroga) 以 9 亿美元的价格出售这家水产养殖公司，然后试图隐藏用所得收益购买的资产，从而欺骗了该公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/china-s-legend-sues-chilean-investor-in-us-over-salmon-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 19:36:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>地区联储调查显示，2024 年美国劳动力市场将降温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/fed-surveys-across-america-show-labor-market-cooling-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据几项地区联邦储备银行的调查，美国雇主预计 2024 年将减少招聘，这一趋势将限制工资增长并降低通胀压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/fed-surveys-across-america-show-labor-market-cooling-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 19:13:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>年终货币市场对美联储退出的担忧与 2018 年紧缩相呼应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/year-end-angst-in-money-markets-echoes-2018-crunch-as-fed-exits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储持续推动消除金融体系的流动性，导致隔夜融资市场的年底交易五年来首次出现波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/year-end-angst-in-money-markets-echoes-2018-crunch-as-fed-exits</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 18:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>另一场顺利拍卖提振信心，美国国债大幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/us-treasuries-jump-as-another-smooth-auction-boosts-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国债券周三上涨，将收益率拖至数月未见的水平，因为对拍卖的强劲需求表明投资者对通胀将继续减速充满信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/us-treasuries-jump-as-another-smooth-auction-boosts-confidence</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 18:29:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
